 | Smart Strike
 | Unarmed 0
 | Offensive (Normal &amp; Crit)
 | Random: HAND, FOOT, HEAD, TORSO, HEAD
 | +5 Accuracy
|-
 | Low Sweep
 | Unarmed 1
 | Offensive (Normal &amp; Crit)
 | Random: FOOT, LOWER_LEG
 | Knockdown duration: 1
|-
 | Darkest Lariat
 | Unarmed 2
 | Offensive (Normal &amp; Crit)
 | Priority: ARM
